vector-skin-desc:
Uheri 2 hacin -i Vector sukū be alibure: 
* 2011 aniya -i ban - Monobook -i neifongge ban, ini arbun getuken, baitalara muten be wesihulembuhebi.
* 2022 aniya -i ban - Uiki Mediya Fulehengge Jihai Isan [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Desktop_Improvements Bodotun -i ban be halame ibebuhe] bodomin -i sindabuha Vevtor sukū.
prefs-vector-enable-vector-1-help: Ereci amasi ududu aniyade, be ulhiyen ulhiyen -i Vector sukū be icemlere. Feingge Vector simbe Vector -i fe ban be baicara be aljambi. (2019 ci aniyai 12 biya de isitala). Ere icemlen de daljingga elei labdu mejige be, bairengge meni [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Reading/Web/Desktop_Improvements bodomin -i afaha] be baicaki.
vector-opt-out-tooltip: Sini sindabun be halafi ere sukū -i fe arbun be baitalara (Fe ban -i Vector)
vector-language-button-aria-label: Gūwa gisun -i araha fiyelen de genere. {{PLURAL:$1|$1 hacin -i gisun}} be baitalaci ojoro.
vector-no-language-button-aria-label: Ere justan ere gisun -i teile taksimbi. Gūwa gisun -i justna be nonggibure
vector-appearance-tooltip: Afaha -i hergen -i jušuru jurhun, onco kemun, jai boco -i arbun be kūbulire
skin-theme-description: [Cendere ban, fonjin dekdere ayoo.] Debais -i dalikū hida ci gabtabuha elden siren be ekiyembure.
skin-theme-exclusion-notice: Ere afaha dubentele gelfiyeken mode de bi.
vector-search-loader: Suwelen -i tucibuhe gisuren be dahime ejeme bi
vector-anon-user-menu-pages: Oron de dosire unde banjibusi -i afaha
vector-anon-user-menu-pages-label: Banjibun de daljingga elei labdu mejige be getuken -i sara
vector-feature-custom-font-size-exclusio: Ere afaha dubentele ajige arbungga hergen be baitalambi
vector-feature-limited-width-exclusion-n: Baktambun muterei teile sini muwašame tuwara tetun -i fa -i onco kemun be jalubumbi.
vector-prefs-limited-width: Jecen bisire onco kemun -i mode be baitalara
vector-prefs-limited-width-help: Hūlara yargiyalame dursulen be muyahūn sain ojoro be dahame, afaha -i onco kemun be kemnere.
empty-language-selector-body: Ere afaha -i baktambun gūwa gisun be urušerakū.
vector-page-tools-unpinned-popup: Agūra hajun -i meniyu be ubade guribuhebi.
vector-appearance-unpinned-popup: Tulergi arbun -i meniyu be ubade guribuhebi.
vector-2022-beta-preview-description: Dalikū akū hūlara muten be bonggode baitalara, ban be halame ibenebure jai tumin bocoi mode -i jergi muten be baktambumbi.
vector-night-mode-gadget-warning: Si ere muten de kamcihakū tumin mode -i ajige agūra hajun be baitalame bi. Bairengge tumin bocoi mode be baitala jalin [[Special:Preferences#mw-prefsection-gadgets|ajige agūra hajun be yaksiki.]]
vector-night-mode-issue-reporting-notice: Tumin bocoi mode de hūlara mangga fonde boolame alambi.
vector-night-mode-issue-reporting-link-l: Tumin bocoi mode -i fonjin be boolame alara
vector-night-mode-issue-reporting-preloa:

Suhe gisun
Bairengge tumin bocoi mode -i boco de ai sere fonjin dekdefi, Uikipediya be hūlara mangga be nirume fisembukini. Bairengge sini bahabuha fonjin -i justan -i fiyelen be nonggibukini.
-->
